output.name: Iron Forge Nest
output.description: Iron Forge Nest is a pioneering technology company based in Seattle, Washington, dedicated to transforming project management through cutting-edge AI innovation. With its flagship product, ScatterShotAI, the company empowers teams by offering an autonomous project management solution that enhances collaboration, drives efficiency, and maintains a strong commitment to AI safety and ethical practices. Emphasizing visionary leadership and operational excellence, Iron Forge Nest is at the forefront of redefining how complex projects are managed in today’s dynamic tech landscape.
